r your patience when we had under-booked enough meals for our staff. .<\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><em>Calum is going to connect you with BBC Events but I will also keep you in mind for any future opportunities. Keen to spread the word about you and work together more.<\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><em><span class=\"s1\">\u00a0<\/span>Best wishes,<\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><em><span class=\"s1\">Hx<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/DSC014451.jpg\" class=\"pretty_image\" data-rel=\"prettyPhoto[7002]\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-7012 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/DSC014451-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"DSC01445\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/DSC014451-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/DSC014451-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/DSC014451-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/DSC014451-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><em><span class=\"s1\">I have just come back from CarFest over in Hampshire where Wayne and Lucy&#8217;s company Red Radish provided the incredible catering.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><em>Wayne has just been put on the suppliers list at the BBC and for good reason, his staff are lovely and his food even lovelier. If you have any upcoming OB\u2019s that need catering then I implore you to contact Wayne first and see what he can do, I can\u2019t recommend him highly enough.<\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><em><span class=\"s1\">\u00a0<\/span>The food is not your average beige Outside Broadcast food, it was tasty and healthy, just a few of the things I had over the week were BBQ Ribs, Stir Fried Pork Lettuce Wrap, Sunday roast and the most incredible Mac &amp; Cheese at the after party.<\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><em><span class=\"s1\">Red Radish<\/span>\u00a0already has a huge following from some of the festivals he does at the moment like Glastonbury, Electric Picnic, Cirque De Soleil, Cannes Film Festival and Feastival.<\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><em>We had a few complications with numbers at the event (from our side, under ordering) but nothing was too much of a bother for him to sort for us.<\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Calum Kean<\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">BBC<\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/images-1.png\" class=\"pretty_image\" data-rel=\"prettyPhoto[7002]\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-7009 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/images-1.png\" alt=\"images-1\" width=\"388\" height=\"88\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/images-1.png 388w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/images-1-300x68.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 388px) 100vw, 388px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If there are two things we really love about \u00a0August on the festival circuit they have to be Carfest Festival and the loveable\u00a0Pudsey Bear. We love catering for a happy&#8230; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/7002\/\"><span class=\"button button-outline button-dark\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> read more <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7372,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[10],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7002","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-customer-references"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized